{"title":"如何本地部署一个Hexo博客","uid":"38b3a078d71e7a950cff95d9511e0633","slug":"how build blog","date":"2024-06-12T01:47:50.514Z","updated":"2023-08-24T01:08:17.527Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/how build blog.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>Hexo是一个快速，简单而强大的博客框架。您可以使用Markdown（或其他语言）编写文章，Hexo可以在几秒钟内生成具有美丽主题的静态文件。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"准备工作\"><a href=\"#准备工作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"准备工作\"></a>准备工作</h2><h3 id=\"安装Git\"><a href=\"#安装Git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Git\"></a>安装<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/\">Git</a></h3><p>最新版的即可。</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装Node-js\"><a href=\"#安装Node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Node.js\"></a>安装<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/\">Node.js</a></h3><p>选择长期维护版(LTS)安装即可。</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装Hexo\"><a href=\"#安装Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Hexo\"></a>安装<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/index.html\">Hexo</a></h3><p>安装Hexo前，请先创建一个Hexo文件夹，创建完成后进入你所创建的文件夹内，右键选择Git Bush Here并进入指令面板，面板上出现的地址就是文件夹路径。<br>复制并粘贴以下代码，回车并等待面板读条结束：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>读条结束后再复制粘贴以下代码，回车并等待读条结束：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo init blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>读条结束后再复制以下代码，回车进入Blog文件夹：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>进入文件夹后再复制以下代码，回车并等待读条结束：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>读条结束后再复制以下代码，回车运行博客并会出现一串网址（出现网址即代表博客创建成功）：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Tip：hexo server可简写成hexo s<br>最后把网址输入至浏览器即可看到Hexo博客最原始的样子，本次部署Hexo过程中遇到了问题请转至此UP视频<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ts4y1f7Gu/?share_source=copy_web&vd_source=9411ff1884155a8ede421e28dc84accc\">超详细！0成本搭建个人网站！！</a><br>更多美化功能我将在闲暇时间进行更新!!!<br>更多美化功能我将在闲暇时间进行更新!!!</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Hexo是一个快速，简单而强大的博客框架。您可以使用Markdown（或其他语言）编写文章，Hexo可以在几秒钟内生成具有美丽主题的静态文件。 准备工作安装Gi...","permalink":"/post/how build blog","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":566,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">准备工作</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Git\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装Git</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Node-js\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装Node.js</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Hexo\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装Hexo</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"Hello World","uid":"b9663f58f18133b35bfe243f3e916a80","slug":"hello-world","date":"2024-06-15T12:40:42.033Z","updated":"2024-06-15T12:40:42.033Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hello-world.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first po